reviewText: But I wasn't bored either. This one can join Orgy Of The Dead in my collection as one I show people who want to see the most freaked out movie ever. I have no idea where this came from, but Todd Sheets produced it so I had to buy it. Must have been early in his career. He should have directed it as well. No gore, no anything really, but a good story and some really odd plot twists. Acting for the leads is good, but the rest is SOOOO bad.
